caption.p: Inhibitory activity of BLF and HLF in the SARS-CoV-2 pseudovirus neutralization assay in different cell lines. (A) Vero E6 cell. (B) Calu-3 cell. (C) 293T cell overexpressing ACE2. Cathepsin L inhibitor E-64d and TMPRSS2 inhibitor camostat mesylate were included as controls in Vero E6 and Calu-3 cells, respectively. IC 50 curve fittings using log 10 (concentration of inhibitors) vs. percentage of DMSO control with variable slopes were performed in Prism 8. All data are mean ± standard deviation of two replicates.
